<item>
            <title>[LU-17837] kfilnd: Set ni_dev_cpt to -1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17837</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;kfilnd defaults ni_dev_cpt to 0. This means that CPT zero is the local CPT (i.e. NUMA node). Until kfilnd properly supports ni_dev_cpt, this should be -1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
